34:39.911 --> 34:43.748
I left a bunch of my shit
at his place at Elohim City.

34:43.748 --> 34:45.083
You know how crazy
they are about

34:45.083 --> 34:46.751
letting people in and all that?

34:46.751 --> 34:49.212
- Uh-huh.
- Yeah. You got a trailer there,

34:49.212 --> 34:51.255
right? Right?

34:51.255 --> 34:54.342
So, you know, maybe
you could vouch for me?

34:54.342 --> 34:56.260
Just, just so
I could get in, you know.

34:56.260 --> 34:59.430
You know, like a woman
to woman kind of thing?

34:59.430 --> 35:02.975
- I don't know.
- Come on.

35:02.975 --> 35:05.478
I'm trying to avoid buying
a whole new wardrobe.

35:09.107 --> 35:11.943
Okay. Yeah. Maybe we can--

35:11.943 --> 35:13.694
I'm not paying you shit.

35:13.694 --> 35:15.530
I had to ask my uncle

35:15.530 --> 35:17.448
redo the cash out to this shop.

35:17.448 --> 35:19.617
That's bullshit.
Dude, no matter what,

35:19.617 --> 35:20.827
- you owe me.
- I'm not trying

35:20.827 --> 35:22.286
to Jew you out of nothing.

35:22.286 --> 35:24.080
- Now, get the fuck out!
- Get back!

35:24.080 --> 35:25.748
- Hey, hey, hey.
- Oh, shit.

35:25.748 --> 35:27.792
- Put the gun away, man.
- Did she say, "gun"?

35:27.792 --> 35:29.752
<i>Stay calm.</i>

35:29.752 --> 35:31.754
Whoa. What happened to her mic?

35:31.754 --> 35:33.381
Dispatch, this is Agent Gram.

35:35.967 --> 35:37.969
Alert local authorities
that there's been gunfire.

35:37.969 --> 35:40.721
Come on,
let's blow this shithole.

35:40.721 --> 35:42.306
Come on.

35:42.306 --> 35:43.891
Keep going.

35:47.770 --> 35:49.981
Where is she going?

35:49.981 --> 35:51.399
What's happening?

36:02.076 --> 36:03.744
Shit.

36:12.170 --> 36:13.629
You heading out?

36:13.963 --> 36:18.968
Ah. I have to get back
to my family.

36:18.968 --> 36:22.722
Well, sure was hoping
you'd stay a little longer.

36:25.349 --> 36:27.018
What is it?

36:27.018 --> 36:29.312
I know what you meant
the other night,

36:29.312 --> 36:31.522
at Passover dinner.

36:33.274 --> 36:36.235
The Lamb, the Lion,

36:36.235 --> 36:37.904
the root of David.

36:38.946 --> 36:40.948
Saying you're a Messiah.

36:40.948 --> 36:43.201
You've been here
for a few weeks now.

36:45.244 --> 36:47.371
What do you think?

36:51.000 --> 36:52.877
I never asked for this.

36:53.336 --> 36:55.046
And I'll be honest,
sometimes it feels

36:55.046 --> 36:56.589
like a burden too great.

36:58.090 --> 36:59.634
But I have been chosen.

37:01.385 --> 37:03.679
And then I was led to you, Livingstone,

37:05.014 --> 37:06.849
because you've been chosen, too.

37:08.017 --> 37:10.144
You've read <i>Revelation.</i>

37:10.686 --> 37:13.231
You know how this old story
ends for me.

37:14.982 --> 37:18.444
God has chosen you to tell
my story when I'm gone.

37:18.444 --> 37:20.029
Why me?

37:21.280 --> 37:24.200
Nobody understands my teachings
like you do.

37:27.161 --> 37:29.080
Where is he?

37:29.080 --> 37:30.623
Where is that son of a bitch?

37:30.623 --> 37:32.959
Hey! What's going on?

37:34.210 --> 37:36.420
This is all your fault.

37:36.420 --> 37:38.297
- You killed her.
- What?

37:38.297 --> 37:39.715
- Killed who?
- Mama!

37:39.715 --> 37:43.469
She's dead.

37:43.469 --> 37:45.263
You are never
coming back to Mount Carmel!

37:45.263 --> 37:47.348
Never!

37:47.348 --> 37:50.142
You goddamn rapist!

37:54.480 --> 37:56.107
Are you okay?

37:59.068 --> 38:00.903
It's already begun.

38:00.903 --> 38:03.906
The forces of darkness trying
to snuff out the light.

38:03.906 --> 38:07.326
Livingstone,
God has asked you to stay

38:07.326 --> 38:09.453
and to fight for that light.

38:15.001 --> 38:17.586
David is Messiah.

38:17.586 --> 38:20.464
<i>The lamb "was slain</i>

38:20.464 --> 38:23.342
<i>and has redeemed us
to God by thy blood."</i>

38:23.342 --> 38:24.635
<i>He will come again</i>

38:24.969 --> 38:27.388
in Judgment...

38:27.388 --> 38:29.557
of the living and the dead.

38:29.557 --> 38:32.768
And his name is David Koresh!

38:33.853 --> 38:35.229
David Koresh.

38:35.229 --> 38:38.232
The name of the lamb
is David Koresh!

38:38.232 --> 38:40.026
When he returns,

38:40.026 --> 38:42.653
he'll bring the kingdom
of heaven to Earth!

38:43.904 --> 38:46.824
The seventh seal will open!

38:46.824 --> 38:49.452
He will slaughter
the Babylonians

38:49.452 --> 38:50.995
and the unbelievers,

38:50.995 --> 38:54.707
pulling down the curtain
on mankind!

38:54.707 --> 38:57.668
The end days are coming.

38:57.668 --> 38:59.879
We will all witness...

39:03.549 --> 39:06.218
She played you, Gary.
She's not gonna call.

39:06.218 --> 39:09.096
- It happens.
- No. She's not doing that.

39:09.096 --> 39:12.016
She's... she's trying.

39:13.434 --> 39:16.145
I know you wanna believe that,
but she's not.

39:16.145 --> 39:18.647
Look, she gave me this letter
in case something went wrong.

39:18.647 --> 39:22.526
Now, why on earth would she do
that if she wasn't serious?

39:22.526 --> 39:24.278
I don't know.

39:24.278 --> 39:27.323
Maybe you should give it a read,
see what she said.

39:36.248 --> 39:38.959
"Hi, Dad.
If you're reading this,

39:38.959 --> 39:41.003
then I'm probably dead.

39:42.588 --> 39:44.799
<i>But if that's true,</i>

39:44.799 --> 39:48.803
<i>it's only because
I was doing something right</i>

39:48.803 --> 39:50.429
<i>for once.</i>

39:52.431 --> 39:54.266
I know I've been
a real disappointment

39:54.266 --> 39:58.229
to you and mom,
but... if you're reading this,

39:58.229 --> 40:00.898
then at least
I died for something important.

40:02.650 --> 40:04.110
Love, Carol."

40:12.952 --> 40:15.704
What if in my blind drive
to make up for the fact

40:15.704 --> 40:18.707
that 76 people died
on my watch,

40:18.707 --> 40:21.085
I go out and get
another one killed?

40:23.921 --> 40:26.924
The people in Elohim City
are scary

40:26.924 --> 40:29.301
and this could go
very badly for her.

40:33.889 --> 40:35.599
I'm gonna go home
to my daughter.

40:35.599 --> 40:36.892
Uh-hmm.

40:36.892 --> 40:38.352
You heading out?

40:39.103 --> 40:40.438
No. I'm gonna stick around,

40:40.438 --> 40:42.481
see if she calls,

40:42.481 --> 40:43.899
if that's okay.

40:45.317 --> 40:47.027
Sure.

40:53.784 --> 40:56.662
<i>Hey, I, I know we were
just gonna pop in and out,</i>

40:56.662 --> 40:58.330
<i>but I kind of need
a place to crash,</i>

40:58.330 --> 40:59.915
so is there any chance

40:59.915 --> 41:01.959
I can stay with you
for a few nights?

41:01.959 --> 41:04.753
Shit. We ain't even there yet

41:04.753 --> 41:07.173
and you're trying
to burrow in like a tick.

41:07.173 --> 41:08.674
You got a crush on me
or something?

41:08.674 --> 41:10.134
No.

41:10.134 --> 41:12.136
- You ain't my type.
- Oh.

41:12.136 --> 41:14.138
I like assholes.

41:15.514 --> 41:17.141
Well, all right by me,

41:17.141 --> 41:18.976
but you'll have to ask
the big guy.

41:40.331 --> 41:41.665
I don't remember checkpoints

41:41.665 --> 41:43.167
last time I was here.

41:43.167 --> 41:44.710
Yeah.
They've been on high alert

41:44.710 --> 41:47.421
since your Wild Bill
and his boys went down.

41:57.681 --> 41:59.850
They have a second gate?

41:59.850 --> 42:03.354
Yeah. This is where
they, uh, search us.

42:39.557 --> 42:40.891
Who the hell are you?

42:40.891 --> 42:42.476
I'm, I'm with Becca.

42:42.476 --> 42:44.853
- I was--
- This is not what I asked.

42:44.853 --> 42:46.897
Who the hell are you?

42:48.607 --> 42:50.067
I'm Carol.

42:50.067 --> 42:51.944
She's Wild Bill's girl.

43:00.286 --> 43:01.704
Get out of the car.

43:01.704 --> 43:03.914
Why?

43:03.914 --> 43:06.458
So I can search you.

43:09.295 --> 43:10.796
Hands up.
You know the deal.

43:27.563 --> 43:29.773
Easy there, perv.

43:40.576 --> 43:43.621
You guys really know how
to make a girl feel welcome.

43:43.621 --> 43:47.625
We do what we can.

43:47.625 --> 43:49.126
Morning, Pappy.

43:49.126 --> 43:51.462
How's training going
with the new recruits?

43:51.462 --> 43:53.422
They'll get there.

43:53.422 --> 43:55.716
Uh, that's my friend Carol.

43:55.716 --> 43:58.594
She wants to see if
she can stay here for a bit,

43:58.594 --> 44:00.346
crash in my trailer.

44:02.056 --> 44:04.725
Nice to meet you, Pappy.

44:04.725 --> 44:06.852
You're Wild Bill's girl.

44:06.852 --> 44:08.062
That's right.

44:08.062 --> 44:09.813
Shame what happened to him.

44:09.813 --> 44:11.649
Yeah. It was messed up.

44:11.649 --> 44:13.984
Yeah. It's just strange,

44:13.984 --> 44:17.279
Wild Bill robbed 21 banks
without a hitch.

44:17.279 --> 44:19.657
And number 22, the cops were
right there waiting for him.

44:19.657 --> 44:22.951
One of his boys was probably
running his mouth.

44:22.951 --> 44:24.328
<i>Nein.</i>

44:24.328 --> 44:25.454
<i>Sitze.</i>

44:31.377 --> 44:33.462
My daddy raised Dobermans,
you know,

44:33.462 --> 44:36.924
beautiful dogs
just like these guys.

44:40.552 --> 44:42.680
Church is at noon.

44:42.680 --> 44:44.682
I wouldn't miss it, Pappy.

45:21.218 --> 45:25.556
theme music plays
